We can determine which the program should follow based on coditions.
## If statment
```java
boolean conditiion = true;

if (condition) {
  //do something
} 
```

## Else if statment
```java
boolean conditiion = true;

if (condition) {
  //do something
} 
```

## Else statment
```java
boolean conditiion = false;

if (condition) {
  //do something
} else {
  //do something
}
```

There is different ways on how to use conditions
## Ways to use conditions
```java
boolean conditiion = true;

if (condition) 
if (condition == true)
if (!condition)
if (condition == false)
```

## Switch statements
```java

swtch
```

